                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - E
                   ====================================

                              Earthlight 128K
                              ===============


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(50119,0) ZXAMPoke(50120,62"}        50119,0:50120,62
@{"Infinite Ammo   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(51708,62)"}        51708,62
@{"Infinite Shields" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(50607,83) ZXAMPoke(50610,62)"}        50607,83:50610,62
@{"Infinite Fuel   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(50668,83) ZXAMPoke(50671,62) ZXAMPoke(50853,83)"}        50668,83:50671,62:50853,83
@{"Land To finish  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49944,195)"}        49944,195

                         I cannot test this POKE on the Amiga as this is a
